  "reference_number": "CTI0012",
  "remarks": "\nDalokay Şanli has held a leadership position in the Kurdistan Workers' Party (PKK) in Europe, and manages recruitment and financing activities for the PKK in Europe. The PKK are a proscribed terrorist organisation in the UK and are listed under the EU’s CP931 Regime.\n",
